2. Click "Add to Chart"
3. Go to Settings (gear icon):
   - Set your preferred timeframe (1H-4H recommended)
   - Adjust threshold (default 60, try 50-70)
   - Configure risk: ATR multiplier (2.5-3.0)
   - Set R/R ratio (default 2.0 for 1:2)
   
4. Strategy Tester:
   - Click "Strategy Tester" tab
   - View Net Profit, % Profitable, Profit Factor
   - Compare vs Buy & Hold
   
5. Optimization:
   - Try different timeframes
   - Adjust threshold for your market
   - Tune risk parameters
   
6. Alerts:
   - Set alerts for "CRYPTONIO Long Signal" and "CRYPTONIO Short Signal"
   - Connect webhook for automated trading (advanced)
   
7. Production Migration:
   - Export logic to Python/Node.js (see Video 18)
   - Connect to exchange API
   - Automate execution

RECOMMENDED SETUPS:

For Bitcoin/ETH (4H):
- Threshold: 65
- ATR Multiplier: 2.5
- R/R Ratio: 2.0

For Altcoins (1H):
- Threshold: 55 (easier to hit)
- ATR Multiplier: 3.0 (wider stops)
- R/R Ratio: 1.5

For Scalping (15M):
- Threshold: 70 (higher quality)
- ATR Multiplier: 2.0
- R/R Ratio: 1.5

*/

